			<h2 class="date-header">March 21, 2012</h2>
	
	<div class="entry-author-david_maurer entry-type-post entry" id="entry-6a00e5506c713988340168e9175f2e970c">

					<h3 class="entry-header"><a href="http://www.flickgym.com/2012/03/dear-apple-facetime-needs-a-way-of-leaving-a-video-message-then-everyone-will-use-it.html"></a></h3>
		
		<div class="entry-content">
			<div class="entry-body">
				<p>Dear Apple... Facetime needs a way of leaving a video message. Then everyone will use it.</p>
			</div>
			
			
		</div>
		<div class="entry-footer">
			<p class="entry-footer-info">
				
